{
  "stem": "15900.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they took him out, and they cut the [? payot ?] and make him work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They make him into a circus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I know them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were going back to the cities, and small towns, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war was over-- to see the parents, and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- and two Germans who was-- well, they came from the First World War.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, when Hitler occupied our city, the old Germans who was in the city before who occupied Poland-- Poland was occupied by Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they say to us--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the ones come back after Hitler took our city, the people who was in Blonie, Warsaw--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The old Germans come back that know everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were friends and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They trusted them, and they were good people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, young people escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we leave to another city, the Nazis come in and the storm troopers come in and take over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're gonna kill you, and arrest you, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One time the two Germans, the good Germans, asked my brother to make slippers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he sent it to families in Germany and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was working with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave us a-- a pass, nobody should take us out for work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're under his supervision.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I walked down for a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I walked down, and the German was talking to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, I don't understand so fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He slapped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He gave me-- he hit me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the blood come out from my ears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my brother saw this through the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He told-- the-- the-- the German-- look, what they're doing to my brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He just went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
